org.ojai.store

Interface Driver


  • @API.Public
 @API.ThreadSafe
public interface Driver
    Entry point of an implementation of OJAI APIs. An OJAI Driver implementation must support JAVA Service Provider Interface. DriverManager uses the implementation to establish a connection to the OJAI data source.
